# Burn & Build — desktop web product

Repo: **`pwa-burn-and-build`** (this workspace)

**Product name:** **Menu planner** (folder/URL alias: `menuplanner/` → redirects). Never use “meal planner” in user-facing copy or docs.

**Site:** burnandbuilddiet.com — desktop browser only. No phone app in this funnel.

---

## Paths

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `landing/` | Marketing → questionnaire |
| `questionnaire/` | **Intake** → save plan → checkout handoff |
| `createyourfoodplan/` | **Checkout paywall** + Stripe return (no intake) |
| `program-report/` | **Unified program shell** — Welcome, Projections, Plan/Servings, Menu planner |
| `menuplanner/` | Redirect → `program-report/?page=menuplanner` |
| `menuplanner/js/planner.js` | Menu planner facade (`plannerState`, `plannerViews`, `plannerPrint`) |
| `mealplanner/` | Legacy URL alias — same redirect as `menuplanner/` |
| `server/` | API + SQLite on Render — programs, per-program Stripe payment |
| `contacts/` | Admin contact list (deployed; key auth) |

**Desktop flow:**
```
Landing → questionnaire → createyourfoodplan (paywall) → program-report (pages 1–4)
```

**Return access:** `burnandbuilddiet.com/menuplanner/` or `program-report/?page=menuplanner` + email → unlock program.

- Each new program = its own Stripe checkout (`programId`).
- **End of product** = Menu planner (page 4 inside program-report).

**Cache busting:** bump `ASSET_VERSION` in `js/assetVersion.js`; `scripts/build-pages.sh` stamps HTML `?v=` at deploy.

---

## Other

- **Signal+** — separate product.
- **Deploy:** push `main` → `.github/workflows/deploy-landing.yml` → GitHub Pages (`scripts/build-pages.sh`).
